The AT&T Database of Faces is available at http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/research/dtg/attarchive/facedatabase.html

In order to install the required files, a shell script can be executed:
$ ./setup_att.sh

This shell script will:
- download att_faces.zip
- unzip att_faces.zip
- convert the .pgm files to .png files
- remove the .pgm files
